Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.38,0:00:36.75,Bengoshi-Credits,Caption,0,0,0,,{\fad(360,360)}Aoi's husband\N Hirano Kohei
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.07,0:00:36.49,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Careful, careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:39.63,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,All right, packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.63,0:00:40.83,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Ko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.20,0:00:42.53,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Ko-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.12,0:00:44.62,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,You're all packed.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.62,0:00:46.33,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Oh. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.33,0:00:48.64,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Crap, it's this late already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.65,0:00:48.64,Bengoshi-Overlap,Kohei,0,0,0,,Crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.64,0:00:50.57,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Here, here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.65,0:00:56.81,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,This business trip \Nis for five days, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.81,0:00:57.27,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.27,0:00:59.84,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,I'll make you your favorite \Nfried shrimp when you get back.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.70,0:01:01.60,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.60,0:01:03.47,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Take care of yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.37,0:01:06.38,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.38,0:01:07.79,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Have a nice trip.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.99,0:01:13.08,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,I better hurry, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.93,0:01:27.90,Bengoshi-Tomoya_Phone,Cell,0,0,0,,Office - Tomoya \N{\b0}Mobile{\b1}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.55,0:01:33.95,Default,Tomoya,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:33.95,0:01:36.36,Default,Tomoya,0,0,0,,What time are you coming home today?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.36,0:01:37.36,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.36,0:01:38.45,Default,Tomoya,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:38.45,0:01:41.14,Default,Tomoya,0,0,0,,Isn't this Kohei-san's—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.14,0:01:42.13,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:42.13,0:01:44.55,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,I thought it was a call \Nfrom your office.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.55,0:01:45.58,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Who was that—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.58,0:01:46.72,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Crap, the bullet train!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.72,0:01:47.39,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,I'm off!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.39,0:01:49.29,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Hey, Ko-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.59,0:02:00.05,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.05,0:02:02.40,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,My office coworker picked \Nup my phone by mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:03.45,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.95,0:02:06.60,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,I see. How did that go?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.44,0:02:10.64,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,It's not too hot?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.64,0:02:11.76,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,It's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.46,0:02:20.48,Default,Lady,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.27,0:02:24.42,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,I'm so sorry. Pardon me.
