Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.05,0:02:50.02,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Hello, Ko-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.02,0:02:52.32,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Why aren't you home yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.32,0:02:55.10,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,You could've at least called \Nto tell me you'd be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.10,0:02:56.39,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.35,0:03:02.15,Bengoshi-Kohei_Phone,Cell screen,0,0,0,,Kohei
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.27,0:03:05.50,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:07.25,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Where are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.25,0:03:08.82,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Aoi, I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.16,0:03:12.05,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Did something happen at work?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.05,0:03:13.53,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Can you come home?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.09,0:03:16.55,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,I'm not coming back.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.55,0:03:17.44,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Let's split up.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.44,0:03:18.52,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.52,0:03:19.90,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,I'm really sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.68,0:03:22.17,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Hold on a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.17,0:03:23.82,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Is it that woman?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.82,0:03:25.76,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Just forget about me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.76,0:03:27.77,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Wait a second!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.35,0:03:30.21,Bengoshi-Kohei_Phone2,Cell top,0,0,0,,Kohei
