Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.22,0:04:00.48,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Kohei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.48,0:04:02.80,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,You forgot this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.80,0:04:04.32,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Oh, my bad. You saved me.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.32,0:04:05.34,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.77,0:04:07.71,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Say, Kohei-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.71,0:04:08.69,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.14,0:04:13.03,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Oh, nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.03,0:04:14.80,Default,Tomomi,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.80,0:04:15.63,Default,Kohei,0,0,0,,You, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.42,0:04:26.47,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.01,0:04:30.21,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.92,0:04:44.17,Default,K,0,0,0,,Aoi-san?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.56,0:04:45.58,Default,Aoi,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.86,0:04:48.69,Default,K,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.69,0:04:51.03,Default,K,0,0,0,,You're not quite yourself today.
