Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.36,0:05:11.76,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,First a cut, then dyeing.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.13,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,Oh, and maybe a perm,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.13,0:05:14.03,Bengoshi-Top,Rina,0,0,0,,and a hair-pack, too.
