Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.03,0:05:14.98,Bengoshi-Top,Y,0,0,0,,All that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.98,0:05:16.55,Bengoshi-Top,Y,0,0,0,,Makes me tired just hearing about it.
