Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.80,0:05:21.13,Default,Y,0,0,0,,The one who really needs\N an image change is this guy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.13,0:05:22.52,Default,Rina,0,0,0,,You can say that again.
